#### Description

This dashboard provides comprehensive visibility into threat intelligence events using the  Infoblox Threat Defense integration. It offers an overview of key threat indicators such as events categorized by Threat Family, Type, and Class, as well as the originating Feed Sources contributing to the SOC insight data.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/infoblox_threat_defense/overview)**
